  <!-- ============ grasper R: single-DOF linkage gripper ============
       mechanism: motor->slider(nut)->crank->parallelogram; 1 master + 8 linear followers
       master  : grasper_R_drive_Joint (crank angle, rad), range [-0.09522, 0.77302], 0 = mesh pose
       opening : d(theta) = 0.0500028*(sin(theta-16.271deg)+0.280184) m  (per-finger tip travel)
         closed  theta=-0.09522   d=-4.5mm  (pads touch)
         zero    theta=0         d= 0
         half    theta=+0.33890  d=+16.76mm
         open    theta=0.77302   d=+37.5mm
       grasper_R_jaw_left/right_Joint are READ-ONLY followers reporting ~= opening (linear approx, max err 0.44mm).
       NOTE SAPIEN/MuJoCo ignore <mimic>: RoboTwin drives followers via embodiment config (see docs/dach_grasper_linkage_design.md);
       MuJoCo uses xml/robot_grasper.xml equality constraints instead. -->
